description:
This is the default compliance policy for Windows Corporate Devices. Assignment is based on the Corporate Devices Azure AD group.

Note: It is not necessary to have a separate group of just Windows corporate devices because this policy will be considered as Non Applicable Corporate Devices members that aren't Windows.

Note: If there are not any compliance policies that apply to a device, the Built-in Device Compliance Policy will generate an error. If there is an assigned, policy, but that policy has no settings defined, it will be considered as Not Applicable, so the built-in policy will still show an error.
